      <section id="home" class="hero-area">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row align-items-center hero-layout">
            <div class="col-lg-7 hero-copy-col">
              <div class="hero-copy">
                <p class="hero-kicker">生活管家到府服務</p>
                <h1>
                  下班累到不想動？<br />
                  清潔、水電、退租整理<br />
                  交給愛拼哞一次處理好
                </h1>
                <p>
                  服務雙北地區，從居家清潔、小型水電，到退租清潔、店面旅宿與特殊場域，先確認需求，再安排合適人力與報價。
                </p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                  <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">立即 LINE 預約</a>
                  <a class="btn btn-dark" href="#services">查看服務方案</a>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-tags" aria-label="服務承諾">
                  <span><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i>2人一組出工</span>
                  <span><i class="far fa-clock"></i>基本4小時服務</span>
                  <span><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i>服務前先確認報價</span>
                  <span><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>完工現場驗收</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5 hero-media-col mt-5 mt-lg-0">
              <div class="hero-card conversion-visual">
                <div class="hero-card-label">愛拼哞生活管家</div>
                <div class="hero-image-wrap hero-brand-visual">
                  <img
                    class="hero-brand-image"
                    src="assets/business-card-front.png"
                    alt="噯拼哞清潔水電修繕品牌主視覺"
                  />
                  <div class="hero-before-after-slot" hidden>
                    <figure data-image-role="before">施工前圖片位置</figure>
                    <figure data-image-role="after">完工後圖片位置</figure>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-mini-tags">
                  <span>2人一組</span>
                  <span>基本4小時</span>
                  <span>完工驗收</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
