      <section class="call-to-action-box no-padding">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="action-style-box">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
              <div class="col-md-8 text-center text-md-left">
                <div class="call-to-action-text">
                  <h3 class="action-title">傳照片，最快初估工時與報價</h3>
                  <p class="action-text">
                    加入官方 LINE，傳現場照片、地址、坪數與需求，我們會先幫你判斷適合的服務項目與預估工時。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4 text-center text-md-right mt-3 mt-md-0">
                <a class="btn btn-light cta-line-btn" href="#contact">立即 LINE 傳照片</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="services" class="services section-padding">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
              <h2 class="section-title">服務方案</h2>
              <h3 class="section-sub-title">先確認現場，再安排合適人力</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row service-card-row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <article class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-broom"></i></div>
                <h3>居家清潔</h3>
                <p>每人每小時 500 元起，2人一組，基本4小時。</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>掃拖、吸塵、除塵</li>
                  <li>家具外觀、廚房外觀</li>
                  <li>浴室基礎清潔</li>
                </ul>
                <a class="service-link" href="#contact">立即詢問</a>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <article class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-spray-can"></i></div>
                <h3>精緻清潔 / 退租清潔</h3>
                <p>每人每小時 700 元起，依現場狀況評估。</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>窗溝、家電外觀</li>
                  <li>浴室細節、廚房油污加強</li>
                  <li>退租入租整理</li>
                </ul>
                <a class="service-link" href="#contact">立即詢問</a>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <article class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i></div>
                <h3>水電修繕 / 生活安裝</h3>
                <p>依項目報價，可先傳照片評估。</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>小型水電</li>
                  <li>電視壁掛、洗衣機架</li>
                  <li>家電架安裝</li>
                </ul>
                <a class="service-link" href="#contact">立即詢問</a>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="scenes" class="facts-area scene-area">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
              <h2 class="section-title">適用場域</h2>
              <h3 class="section-sub-title">不同空間，用不同方式處理</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row scene-list">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>居家住宅</h3>
                <p>日常維護、浴室廚房清潔、定期清潔。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>分租套房</h3>
                <p>退租入租、公共區域、房東交屋前整理。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>旅宿飯店</h3>
                <p>房務清潔、定期維護、營業空間整理。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>店面商空</h3>
                <p>營業前後、地板清潔、環境整理。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>夜場空間</h3>
                <p>營業後整理、地面清潔、廁所與公共區域。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>工廠倉庫</h3>
                <p>大坪數環境、堆放區、動線與角落整理。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>醫療院所</h3>
                <p>候診區、診間周邊、營業空間維護。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
              <article class="scene-card">
                <h3>學校健身房</h3>
                <p>公共空間、器材周邊、使用後環境整理。</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="quote" class="section-padding quote-method">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
              <h2 class="section-title">報價方式</h2>
              <h3 class="section-sub-title">依服務範圍與現場狀況評估</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
              <div class="quote-card">
                <span>01</span>
                <h3>照片初估</h3>
                <p>一般居家、小店面、小型水電修繕，可先提供坪數、照片、地點區域與希望服務時間。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
              <div class="quote-card">
                <span>02</span>
                <h3>現場估價</h3>
                <p>裝潢後、垃圾屋、工廠、醫療院所、大坪數或需清運消毒的案件，建議到場確認。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 mb-4">
              <div class="quote-card">
                <span>03</span>
                <h3>定期維護</h3>
                <p>店面、旅宿、公共空間或長期需求，可依頻率與範圍規劃維護方式。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="cases" class="section-padding cases-area">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-compact" id="caseEmptyState">
            <div>
              <h2 class="section-title">完工案例</h2>
              <h3>真實案例陸續整理中</h3>
              <p>完工照片將經客戶同意後公開。預約前可先透過 LINE 了解可提供的服務紀錄。</p>
            </div>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">LINE 詢問案例</a>
          </div>
          <div class="row case-grid" id="caseGrid" hidden></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="process" class="content section-padding process-area">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row align-items-start">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h3 class="column-title">預約流程</h3>
              <div class="process-steps">
                <div class="process-step">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4>加 LINE 傳需求</h4>
                    <p>提供地址、服務類型與希望時段。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="process-step">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4>傳照片初估</h4>
                    <p>用現場照片快速判斷範圍、人力與工時。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="process-step">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4>確認時間與報價</h4>
                    <p>確認服務內容、時間、人員與注意事項。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="process-step">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4>到府施作並驗收</h4>
                    <p>完工後現場確認成果，再完成交付。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 mt-5 mt-lg-0">
              <h3 class="column-title">常見問題</h3>
              <div class="faq-box">
                <article>
                  <h4>可以直接給價格嗎？</h4>
                  <p>一般小型案件可用照片初估。特殊場域、垃圾屋、裝潢後或大面積案件，建議現場估價。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                  <h4>清潔和水電可以一起約嗎？</h4>
                  <p>可以先一起詢問，會依需求判斷是否同一天處理或分時段安排。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                  <h4>大型場域可以處理嗎？</h4>
                  <p>可先提供照片、坪數、使用狀況與希望完成時間，再評估人力與方式。</p>
                </article>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="contact-area section-padding">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
              <h2 class="section-title">聯絡我們</h2>
              <h3 class="section-sub-title">把需求傳給噯拼哞</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
              <div class="contact-info-box">
                <span class="contact-line-label">官方 LINE 優先</span>
                <h3>@619jqlpd</h3>
                <p>傳現場照片、地址與需求，比電話描述更快判斷工時與報價。</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                  <li><i class="fab fa-line"></i><span>@619jqlpd</span></li>
                  <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i><span>台北市 / 新北市</span></li>
                  <li><i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i><a href="tel:0229096923">02-29096923</a></li>
                </ul>
                <a class="btn btn-primary contact-line-btn" href="#contact">立即 LINE 預約</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 mt-5 mt-lg-0">
              <form class="contact-form" id="serviceForm">
                <div class="form-row">
                  <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                    <label for="name">姓名</label>
                    <input class="form-control" id="name" type="text" name="name" autocomplete="name" required />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                    <label for="phone">聯絡電話</label>
                    <input class="form-control" id="phone" type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" required />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="service">服務項目</label>
                  <select class="form-control" id="service" name="service" required>
                    <option value="">請選擇項目</option>
                    <option>居家清潔</option>
                    <option>水電修繕</option>
                    <option>裝潢後清潔</option>
                    <option>垃圾屋清潔</option>
                    <option>店面清潔</option>
                    <option>旅宿清潔</option>
                    <option>夜場清潔</option>
                    <option>醫療院所清潔</option>
                    <option>健身房清潔</option>
                    <option>防滑鍍膜</option>
                    <option>寵物保姆</option>
                    <option>其他需求</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="message">需求說明</label>
                  <textarea
                    class="form-control"
                    id="message"
                    name="message"
                    rows="5"
                    placeholder="例如：退租清潔約 20 坪，浴室水垢較重，希望週六上午處理。"
                    required
                  ></textarea>
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">整理諮詢內容</button>
                <p class="form-note" id="formNote" role="status"></p>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer id="footer" class="footer bg-overlay">
        <div class="footer-main">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-between">
              <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6 footer-widget footer-about">
                <div class="footer-brand">
                  <img src="assets/logo.jpg" alt="噯拼哞標誌" />
                  <div>
                    <h3>噯拼哞</h3>
                    <p>清潔 × 水電修繕 × 生活管家</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p>居家、商用與特殊場域皆可先詢問，依需求安排清潔、修繕與生活協助服務。</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 footer-widget mt-5 mt-md-0">
                <h3 class="widget-title">服務項目</h3>
                <ul class="list-arrow">
                  <li>居家清潔</li>
                  <li>水電修繕</li>
                  <li>裝潢後清潔</li>
                  <li>完工案例</li>
                  <li>特殊場域清潔</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 footer-widget mt-5 mt-lg-0">
                <h3 class="widget-title">聯絡資訊</h3>
                <div class="working-hours">
                  電話：02-29096923<br />
                  官方 LINE：@619jqlpd<br />
                  服務範圍：台北市 / 新北市<br />
                  諮詢時請先提供照片與地點
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="copyright">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
              <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                <div class="copyright-info">噯拼哞 © 2026</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>

      <div id="back-to-top" data-spy="affix" data-offset-top="10" class="back-to-top position-fixed">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" title="回到上方">
          <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="constra/plugins/jQuery/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="constra/plugins/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="constra/plugins/slick/slick.min.js"></script>
    <script src="constra/plugins/slick/slick-animation.min.js"></script>
    <script src="constra/js/script.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
